TextEng: Farewell.
Anything new you know?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Is the creature justified? Neverwinter would've used it in a spell.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그 생명체가 확인된 건가요? 네버윈터라면 주문에 사용했을 텐데요.

TextEng: Me want talk about reward.
Go over the basic run down of the area.
Text: 지역에 대한 기본적인 상황을 설명해 주세요.

TextEng: A Waterdhavian creature was in another district. Think there's one here?
Text: 워터딥의 생명체가 다른 지구에 있었어요. 여기도 있을 것 같나요?

TextEng: Are there any safe locations in the district?
Is there an identifiable enemy behind this?
If I find out anything I'll let you know.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Are the undead linked to the plague? When did this start?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 언데드가 역병과 관련 있나요? 이게 언제 시작된 거죠?

TextEng: You know a bossman behind the dead?
Text: 죽은 놈들 뒤에 대장이 있는 거 알아?

TextEng: There safe places in this district?
Water-whosian creature found in other district. One here maybe?
Text: 물-뭐시기 생명체 다른 지구에서 발견됐어. 여기도 있어?

TextEng: Me see what me find.
You go over simple stuff about area.
Text: 너 이 지역 간단한 거 설명해.

TextEng: Me go now.
Have you had any updates? Any new information?
Text: 새로운 소식 있나요? 새로 알게 된 정보는요?

TextEng: Tell me about the Sword Coast Boys.
Text: 검 해안의 패거리에 대해 말해 주세요.

TextEng: You tell about local Cult thingy.
Tell me about this local Cult.
Text: 이 지역 사교에 대해 말해 주세요.

TextEng: You tell about Sword Coast Boys.
Text: 너 검 해안의 패거리 얘기 해줘.

TextEng: Me tough and scary. You give more!
I'm very dangerous, and worth more than that.
Text: 전 아주 위험한 사람이고, 그것보다 더 가치가 있어요.

TextEng: Am I to be rewarded for my efforts?
Me get reward for doing stuff?
I found the Waterdhavian Yuan-Ti creature. It raised the zombies.
Text: 워터딥의 유안티 생명체를 찾았어요. 그게 좀비를 일으켰어요.

TextEng: Me find Water-daisy creature. Snake Lady. It caused dead problems.
Text: 나 물-데이지 생명체 찾았어. 뱀 여자. 놈이 죽은 것들 문제 일으켰어.

TextEng: Reward time. Cough something up or I get nasty.
Text: 보상 받을 시간이에요. 뭐라도 내놓든지 아니면 가만 안 둘 거예요.

TextEng: Me break faces if no get reward now!
Text: 나 지금 보상 안 주면 얼굴 박살 낼 거야!

TextEng: Farewell.
Bye bye.
Thanks. Farewell.
Me thank you. Bye bye.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now. Don't I deserve more than that?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 자, 이봐요. 그것보다는 더 받아야 하는 거 아니에요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me deserve more. You think so, right?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 더 받을 자격 있어. 그치?

TextEng: I wanted to discuss the reward?
<FullName> is my name. I'm helping Aribeth.
Me <FullName>. Me help Aribeth.
What is my name to you? Why should I tell you?
Text: 제 이름이 당신한테 무슨 의미죠? 왜 말해야 하는데요?

TextEng: Why you care what name me gots? Why me tell you?
Text: 내 이름이 왜 궁금해? 왜 말해야 해?

TextEng: I've no time to speak right now. Farewell.
Text: 지금 얘기할 시간 없어요. 안녕히 계세요.

TextEng: Me gots no time for you. Bye bye.
Do you know anything about the Waterdhavian creatures?
Text: 워터딥의 생명체들에 대해 아는 거 있나요?

TextEng: You know anything about Water-whosian creature things?
I killed the creature that caused the undead.
Me kill creature that caused undead.
Back to my other questions.
Back to other questions, okay?
What rumors you hear?
What rumors have you heard?
Who you?
Who are you?
Who you be?
Who are you? What is your role here?
